    "body": "> But a malicious miner still spends nothing to attempt such spam attack\n\nYou'll waste electricity, but yes, nothing else. And again you need **a lot** of luck. Secondly; don't forget you have to be very rich to \"spam\" in one block (+ block gas limit you have to take in to consideration).\n\nEDIT: A larger issue is if the miner had 51% of the network power in which case you could spam in multiple blocks. But we'll have larges issues if there's a 51% attack. \n",
